net.richarddawkins.watchmaker.app

Interface AppData

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ArthromorphSwingAppData, ColourSwingAppData, MonochromeSwingAppData, SnailSwingAppData, SwingAppData

    public interface AppData
    An instance of AppData provides a facade representing an instance of a Watchmaker session which deals with one particular subclass of Morph. An AppData instance is associated with an instance of MorphConfig: this association bridges the gap between Watchmaker application logic and presentation logic.
    Author:
    Alan Canon
